Felicitations have begun to pour in for Nollywood actor and filmmaker, Alesh Ola Sanni as he announced the acquisition of a new home. The crossover actor took to his Instagram page to share pictures of his newly built house. Sanni revealed that the house has been under construction since 2018. He made this known with a step by step images from scratch to finish.   Academy announces presenters as 64th Grammy holds today     ID Cabasa, Naija Ninja complete late Sound Sultan’s 9th…     Darey Art Alade speaks as The Real Housewives Of Lagos…   He wrote: “first birthday gift from me to myself. I appreciate myself so much before anybody else will. This is really a gift that I’ve been waiting for and I’m grateful for it and hope for more Insha Allahu.” Meanwhile, Alesh’s colleagues including Mercy Aigbe, Rotimi Salami, Khadijat Ayoade, Faithia Williams, and Nkechi Blessing have taken to the actor’s page to congratulate the father of one.